[Measure Source Pull Capability Statement](CapabilityStatement-MeasureSourcePull.html).Feature: MeasureSource-3 A Measure Source that implements the Pull Option shall provide a CapabilityStatement when queried via [base]/metadata.Feature: MeasureSource-4 A Measure Source that implements the Push Option shall conform to the
